{"tid":2012396,"cid":10,"subCid":0,"title":"Square Enix為鼓勵防疫推出集結54款遊戲內容的巨無霸組合包 售價一千出頭、收入做公益","createTime":"2020-05-11T14:56:52.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-11T15:38:19.000Z","uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"45f9779264dc87e7da77c4c0d80e2f6fb41897db","tid":2012396,"uid":135867,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"Square Enix 為鼓勵疫情期間玩家能夠「待在家盡情玩」，在 PC 遊戲平台 Steam 推出「Square Enix Eidos Anthology」巨無霸組合包，打出 0.5 折讓玩家花新台幣一千多元就可以一口氣擁有 54 款遊戲內容。<br />\n <br />\nimage<br />\n <br />\n　　Square Enix 表示，他們希望透過「待在家盡情玩」活動鼓勵玩家保持社交距離，並在這艱難的時刻，盡力對慈善機構提供協助。因此他們釋出此項組合包，讓玩家以划算價格購買精彩的遊戲作品，並將收益全數捐給北美與歐洲的食物銀行和其他慈善機構。<br />\n <br />\n　　在這「Square Enix Eidos Anthology」巨無霸組合包中，包括《古墓奇兵》系列、《正當防衛（Just Cause）》系列、《末日危城》系列與《駭客入侵》系列等，詳細遊戲內容名單可參考 Steam 網頁說明。<br />\n <br />\nimage<br />\nimage<br />\n《古墓奇兵》<br />\n　　「Square Enix Eidos Anthology」巨無霸組合包 54 款內容原價 24,254 元，打 0.5 折後，售價為 1,190 元。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://store.steampowered.com/agecheck/bundle/14956\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstore.steampowered.com%2Fagecheck%2Fbundle%2F14956&d=4ZfQOx7HBA0d%2BjGm5r97Haha%2BoeUeRXR1jLQ0PybHu0%3D&h=1f6c0a19\" target=\"_blank\">https://store.steampowered.com/agecheck/bundle/14956</a>"},{"pid":"71ab646bb4d50bd7d79bd7c177c5313735d0c1cc","tid":2012396,"uid":191926,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:04:00.000Z","msg":"末日危城 原來同 se 有關<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n十幾年前 玩過1同2"},{"pid":"642dbabda9e76c7cd9393716912fd5e587e23cc8","tid":2012396,"uid":34869,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:04:13.000Z","msg":"好多尖奶羅拉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"66f0943f8d311d708e88a14ce9b44efb7884e315","tid":2012396,"uid":109923,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-11T15:07:59.000Z","msg":"台幣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.